Package: sparr
Type: Package
Title: Spatial and Spatiotemporal Relative Risk
Version: 2.2-01
Date: 2018-02-22
Authors@R: c(
  person(c("Tilman", "M."), "Davies", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "tdavies@maths.otago.ac.nz"),
  person(c("Jonathan", "C."), "Marshall", role = c("aut"), email = "j.c.marshall@massey.ac.nz"))
Description: Provides functions to estimate kernel-smoothed spatial and spatio-temporal densities and relative risk functions, and perform subsequent inference.
